camsniff (1.0.2-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Enable all features by default in configuration
  * Add Web UI and IoT enumeration dependencies to debian/control
  * Improve SNMP temp file handling for non-root runs
  * Keep Makefile default config in sync with env_setup
  * Switch to debhelper-compat (= 12) and set Rules-Requires-Root: no
  * Add debian/source/format (3.0 native); bump Standards-Version 4.7.0
  * Harden banner animations for non-TTY environments

